[%- FILTER collapse %]
<i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;Information<br>This is the <a
href="[% conf.root %]secure/rep/">Admin</a> area for representatives of DATA
member societies. If you have access to this area, then you can update the
information held about <a href="[% conf.root %]secure/rep/events">Events</a>
associated with the member

[%~ MACRO whatson_societies BLOCK %]

[%~ IF societies.size == 1 # Must be a representative of a single society -%]

society that you represent as well as the details of that <a href="
[%~ conf.root %]secure/rep/societies">Society</a>.

[%~ ELSE # Must be a representative of more than one society =%]

societies that you represent as well as the details of those <a href="
[%~ conf.root %]secure/rep/societies">Societies</a>.

[%~ END # IF societies.size == 1 %]

[%~ END # MACRO whatson_societies BLOCK %]

[%~ CGIAPP.embed(
    'whatson_societies',
    'filter' = {
        'userid' => "$session.userid"
    }
) %]

[%~ END ~%]
